      <title>最高法院坚持我们对“幽灵枪”套件的监管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/supreme-court-upholds-us-regulation-of-ghost-gun-kits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院维持了联邦内置的“幽灵枪”套件的法规，支持在拜登政府期间制定的一项规则，以阻止官员们说的是不可追踪的武器的洪流。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/supreme-court-upholds-us-regulation-of-ghost-gun-kits</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 14:09:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CBO说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/us-treasury-risks-payment-default-as-soon-as-august-cbo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国会预算办公室警告说，如果立法者未能提高或中止债务限额，联邦政府可能会在八月的时间内用完足够的钱来按时支付所有账单。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/us-treasury-risks-payment-default-as-soon-as-august-cbo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 14:03:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其的反对派猛烈抨击中央银行在动荡的干预中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/turkey-opposition-slams-central-bank-over-turmoil-intervention</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其的主要反对党指责中央银行为政府提供掩护，以帮助管理上周拘留伊斯坦布尔市长的财务影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/turkey-opposition-slams-central-bank-over-turmoil-intervention</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 13:54:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡尼在贸易战中承诺为加拿大汽车行业数十亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/carney-pledges-billions-for-canadian-auto-sector-in-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自由党的领导人马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）承诺将有20亿加元（14亿美元）的“战略响应基金”，以帮助加拿大汽车制造业，并加强受到美国关税威胁的供应链。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/carney-pledges-billions-for-canadian-auto-sector-in-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 13:53:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>邦迪将委内瑞拉驱逐出境归咎于法官的“矛盾”命令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/bondi-blames-deportation-fight-on-judge-s-contradictory-orders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总检察长帕姆·邦迪（Pam Bondi）否认，政府违反了一名联邦法官的命令，反对被指控的委内瑞拉帮派成员驱逐出境，而是指责他发出“矛盾的”口头和书面裁决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/bondi-blames-deportation-fight-on-judge-s-contradictory-orders</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 13:37:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大西洋发布有关胡塞攻击的完整信号文本链</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/atlantic-releases-details-of-signal-text-chain-on-houthi-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大西洋发布了美国顶级官员之间关于信号的小组聊天的笔录，这是无意中的编辑，揭示了国防部长皮特·赫格斯（Pete Hegseth）如何分享时机和武器系统的细节，这些细节和武器系统被用于对也门激进分子的攻击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/atlantic-releases-details-of-signal-text-chain-on-houthi-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 13:05:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯在英国增长降级后公布了140亿英镑的维修工作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/reeves-says-labour-has-rebuilt-uk-headroom-to-9-9-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯（Rachel Reeves）的总理在英国对本年度的增长预测后，削减了140亿英镑（180亿美元）的财政室，并削减了福利和政府支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/reeves-says-labour-has-rebuilt-uk-headroom-to-9-9-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 12:50:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>万斯加入了格陵兰巡回演唱会，正如特朗普所说的“我们需要的”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/vances-new-greenland-travel-plans-offer-relief-for-denmark</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首先是唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump Jr）宣布，他的父亲说美国将吞并世界上最大的岛屿之后，他几周后“热火”到格陵兰。现在，副总统JD Vance正在那里参加旅行，因为他不希望他的妻子“独自获得所有乐趣”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/vances-new-greenland-travel-plans-offer-relief-for-denmark</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 09:07:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在数周而不是几个月内权衡铜进口关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/trump-may-implement-copper-import-tariffs-within-weeks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉此事的人们说，美国对铜进口的关税可能会在几周内，比判决的截止日期提前几个月。在纽约交易的铜升至纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/trump-may-implement-copper-import-tariffs-within-weeks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 01:06:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国摇摆以取代特朗普裁定的亚洲美国国际开发署的努力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/as-trump-cuts-aid-china-flows-funds-to-strategic-corner-of-asia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国在2月下旬取消了两个在柬埔寨的援助项目。一个是鼓励儿童识字，另一个是为了改善五岁以下儿童的营养和发展。一周后，中国援助机构宣布为实现几乎相同目标的计划提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/as-trump-cuts-aid-china-flows-funds-to-strategic-corner-of-asia</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 00:49:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
